import '@material/react-button/index.scss';
import { Button } from '@material/react-button';
import '@material/react-text-field/index.scss';
import TextField from '@material/react-text-field';
import { useState } from 'react';
import { Grid } from '@material/react-layout-grid';

const initializeFValues = {
    fullName: '',
    rollNo: '',
    studentClass: '',
    totalSubjects: '',
    age: ''
}

function StudentRecordForm(props){
    const [values, setValues] = useState(initializeFValues);
    
        return(
            <form>
                <Grid container>
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                    <label>
                        Full Name:
                        <input type="text" name="fullName" />
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        Rollno:
                        <input type="text" name="rollNo" />
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        Student Class:
                        <input type="text" name="studentClass" />
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        Total Subjects:
                        <input type="text" name="totalSubject" />
                    </label>
                    <label>
                        Age:
                        <input type="text" name="age" />
                    </label>
                    <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </form>
        )
}

export default StudentRecordForm;
